title: Box And Cover, late 19th–early 20th century
creditline: Gift of Mr. and Mrs. Arthur Wiesenberger
description: Square black lacquer box (a); square black lacquer lid (b) with deep sides, slightly domed top having gilded decoration of five circular crests and foliate scrolling.
